name: highschooler
0:
”Alexa, ask high school week planner to begin game”
”tell me activities on Monday”
”what's up this week”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: high school week planner
des: As a high school student, one has to juggle many conflicting priorities such as school, part-time work and activities for fun. Every week the player have fixed number of free hours for school, work and fun activities and the player has to choose how to allocate those free times. By the end of each week a summary report will be provided to show how well/poor they did.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
